      <a href="/blog/forests/update-santander-admits-its-funding-forest-destruction-20150212"><img src="http://www.greenpeace.org.uk/sites/files/gpuk/imagecache/group_post_thumbnail/images/santander%20one%20year%20ago.jpg" alt="" title=""  class="imagecache imagecache-group_post_thumbnail imagecache-default imagecache-group_post_thumbnail_default" width="125" height="87" /></a>
